      "px950201_rand_impacts_of_covid19_coronavirus_likely_origin_opt_5": "Not sure",
      "sec_please_indicate_whether_you_think_these__title": "Please indicate whether you think these questions are true or false.",
      "px950201_rand_impacts_of_covid19_coronavirus_belief_exposure_spread": "People exposed to coronavirus (COVID-19) can spread the disease to others, even if they do not have any symptoms.",
      "px950201_rand_impacts_of_covid19_coronavirus_belief_5g_radiation": "The symptoms of coronavirus (COVID-19) are connected to 5G mobile network radiation.",
      "px950201_rand_impacts_of_covid19_coronavirus_belief_washing_protection": "Regularly washing your hands for 20 seconds can help protect you from the coronavirus.",
      "sec_attitudes_towards_various_government_and_title": "Attitudes towards various government and private institutions can range from distrust to trust. Using a scale from 0 to 10, where 0 indicates complete distrust and 10 indicates complete trust, please indicate your level of trust in:",
